7. **`org.jsoup.helper.StringUtil:normaliseWhitespace(Ljava/lang/String;)Ljava/lang/String;`** - This utility method is used to normalize whitespace in strings. If it does not handle whitespace correctly, it could lead to discrepancies in the output.
